MOVE ZTT_CL_V_DEP_C-ACCOUNT_NO TO
ZTT_CL_DEPE_C-ACCOUNT_NO .
MOVE ZTT_CL_V_DEP_C-MANDT TO
ZTT_CL_DEPE_C-MANDT .
